>}\n <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>{<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"否\"</span>}\n}\n</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n','1. 在el-table-column标签中加入 :formatter=\"formate\"\n2. 在methods中添加方法 formate\n3. 方法如下\n```\nformate(val)\n{\n	if(val==0){return \"是\"}\n	else{return \"否\"}\n}\n```',0,1,1,0,1,'vue2.0的Element UI的表格table把数字格式化为其他内容','vue2.0的Element UI的表格table把数字格式化为其他内容',0,'2018-10-11 10:00:34','2018-10-11 10:00:34'),(34,'ubuntu 同步 ntp',1,'',NULL,1,'<ol>\n<li>安装ntp客户端<code>apt-get install ntpdate</code></li>\n<li>ntpdate ip地址</li>\n</ol>\n','1. 安装ntp客户端`apt-get install ntpdate`\n2. ntpdate ip地址',0,3,1,0,1,'ubuntu 同步 ntp','ubuntu 同步 ntp',0,'2018-10-12 13:11:53','2018-10-12 13:11:53'),(35,'springboot集成swagger',1,'zhyd/cover/20181012132349156.png',NULL,1,'<ol>\n<li>引入依赖<pre><code><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">springfox-swagger2.version</span>&gt;</span>2.2.2<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">springfox-swagger2.version</span>&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>io.springfox<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>springfox-swagger2<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">version</span>&gt;</span>${springfox-swagger2.version}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">version</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>io.springfox<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">groupId</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>springfox-swagger-ui<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">artifactId</span>&gt;</span>\n         <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">version</span>&gt;</span>${springfox-swagger2.version}<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">version</span>&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">dependency</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>添加配置类</p>\n<pre><code>     <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Configuration</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@EnableSwagger</span>2\n     <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"hljs-class\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">SwaggerConfig</span> </span>{\n         <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**\n          * 可以注入多个doket，也就是多个版本的api，可以在看到有三个版本groupName不能是重复的，v1和v2是ant风格匹配，配置文件\n      * api查看地址:http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html\n      * <span class=\"hljs-doctag\">@return</span>\n      */</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-meta\">@Bean</span>\n     <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">public</span> Docket <span class=\"hljs-title\">api</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> </span>{\n         <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//可以添加多个header或参数</span>\n         ParameterBuilder aParameterBuilder = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ParameterBuilder();\n         aParameterBuilder\n                 .parameterType(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"header\"</span>)\n                 .name(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"Authorization\"</span>)\n                 .description(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"header中Authorization字段用于认证\"</span>)\n                 .modelRef(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ModelRef(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"string\"</span>))\n                 <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//非必需，这里是全局配置，然而在登陆的时候是不用验证的</span>\n                 .required(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">false</span>).build();\n         List&lt;Parameter&gt; aParameters = <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ArrayList&lt;Parameter&gt;();\n         aParameters.add(aParameterBuilder.build());\n                     <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> Docket(DocumentationType.SWAGGER_2).groupName(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"v1\"</span>).select().apis(RequestHandlerSelectors.basePackage(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"com.weishilvjian.freapi.controller\"</span>))\n                         .paths(PathSelectors.any()).build().apiInfo(apiInfo1()).globalOperationParameters(aParameters);\n         <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//                ;</span>\n             }\n\n         <span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">private</span> ApiInfo <span class=\"hljs-title\">apiInfo1</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">()</span> </span>{\n             <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">new</span> ApiInfoBuilder()\n                     .title(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"sihuatech  api\"</span>)\n                     .contact(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"wjh\"</span>)\n                     .version(<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"v0.01\"</span>)\n                     .build();\n         }\n\n     }\n</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>使用<br> 在controller类上添加注解:<code>@Api(value = &quot;用来提供FRE,FCE以及OCR等接口&quot;)</code><br> 在方法上添加注解(我的参数格式是@RequestBody JSONObject param这样的,其它格式的请参照网上教程):<br> `@ApiOperation(value=&quot;FCE接口&quot;, notes=&quot;json格式参数&quot;,produces = &quot;application/json&quot;)<br> @ApiImplicitParams({</p>\n<pre><code>     @<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">ApiImplicitParam</span>(<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">name</span>=\"<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">param</span>\",<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">value</span>= <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"{\\\"mobile\\\":\\\"17765071662\\\",\\\"passWord\\\":\\\"123456\\\"}\"</span>,dataType=<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"string\"</span>, paramType = <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"body\"</span>)})`\n</code></pre></li>\n<li>效果如下图:<br><img src=\"http://pdlmj6kjo.bkt.clouddn.com/2018-10-12_131907.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ol>\n','1. 引入依赖\n```\n<springfox-swagger2.version>2.2.2</springfox-swagger2.version>\n<dependency>\n            <groupId>io.springfox</groupId>\n            <artifactId>springfox-swagger2</artifactId>\n            <version>${springfox-swagger2.version}</version>\n        </dependency>\n        <dependency>\n            <groupId>io.springfox</groupId>\n            <artifactId>springfox-swagger-ui</artifactId>\n            <version>${springfox-swagger2.version}</version>\n        </dependency>\n```\n2. 添加配置类\n```\n		@Configuration\n		@EnableSwagger2\n		public class SwaggerConfig {\n			/**\n			 * 可以注入多个doket，也就是多个版本的api，可以在看到有三个版本groupName不能是重复的，v1和v2是ant风格匹配，配置文件\n		 * api查看地址:http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html\n		 * @return\n		 */\n		@Bean\n		public Docket api() {\n			//可以添加多个header或参数\n			ParameterBuilder aParameterBuilder = new ParameterBuilder();\n			aParameterBuilder\n					.parameterType(\"header\")\n					.name(\"Authorization\")\n					.description(\"header中Authorization字段用于认证\")\n					.modelRef(new ModelRef(\"string\"))\n					//非必需，这里是全局配置，然而在登陆的时候是不用验证的\n					.required(false).build();\n			List<Parameter> aParameters = new ArrayList<Parameter>();\n			aParameters.add(aParameterBuilder.build());\n						return new Docket(DocumentationType.SWAGGER_2).groupName(\"v1\").select().apis(RequestHandlerSelectors.basePackage(\"com.weishilvjian.freapi.controller\"))\n							.paths(PathSelectors.any()).build().apiInfo(apiInfo1()).globalOperationParameters(aParameters);\n			//                ;\n				}\n\n			private ApiInfo apiInfo1() {\n				return new ApiInfoBuilder()\n						.title(\"sihuatech  api\")\n						.contact(\"wjh\")\n						.version(\"v0.01\")\n						.build();\n			}\n\n		}\n```\n\n3. 使用\n	在controller类上添加注解:`@Api(value = \"用来提供FRE,FCE以及OCR等接口\")`\n	在方法上添加注解(我的参数格式是@RequestBody JSONObject param这样的,其它格式的请参照网上教程):\n	`@ApiOperation(value=\"FCE接口\", notes=\"json格式参数\",produces = \"application/json\")\n    @ApiImplicitParams({\n            @ApiImplicitParam(name=\"param\",value= \"{\\\"mobile\\\":\\\"17765071662\\\",\\\"passWord\\\":\\\"123456\\\"}\",dataType=\"string\", paramType = \"body\")})`\n4. 效果如下图:\n![](http://pdlmj6kjo.bkt.clouddn.com/2018-10-12_131907.png)',0,2,1,0,1,'springboot集成swagger','springboot集成swagger',0,'2018-10-12 13:23:49','2018-10-12 13:23:49'),(36,' Java泛型中<？ extends E>和<？ super E>的区别',1,'zhyd/cover/20181018173405703.jpg',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/asdfsadfasdfsa/article/details/52794573?utm_source=blogxgwz4\">https://blog.csdn.net/asdfsadfasdfsa/article/details/52794573?utm_source=blogxgwz4</a></p>\n','https://blog.csdn.net/asdfsadfasdfsa/article/details/52794573?utm_source=blogxgwz4',0,2,1,0,0,'Java泛型中<？ extends E>和<？ super E>的区别','Java泛型中<？ extends E>和<？ super E>的区别',0,'2018-10-18 17:34:06','2018-10-18 17:34:06'),(37,'定时将ubuntu上的mysql数据库备份到github',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://icharle.com/Linuxbak.html\">https://icharle.com/Linuxbak.html</a></p>\n','https://icharle.com/Linuxbak.html',0,3,1,0,0,'定时将ubuntu上的mysql数据库备份到github','定时将ubuntu上的mysql数据库备份到github',0,'2018-10-18 18:45:31','2018-10-18 18:45:31'),(38,'maven引入本地jar包',1,'',NULL,1,'<p>1.先将jar包安装到本地仓库<br>mvn install:install-file -Dfile=jar包的位置 -DgroupId=上面的groupId -DartifactId=上面的artifactId -Dversion=上面的version -Dpackaging=jar </p>\n<ol>\n<li>在pom文件中添加依赖就可以了,跟安装到本地仓库的版本要一致.</li>\n</ol>\n','1.先将jar包安装到本地仓库\nmvn install:install-file -Dfile=jar包的位置 -DgroupId=上面的groupId -DartifactId=上面的artifactId -Dversion=上面的version -Dpackaging=jar \n2. 在pom文件中添加依赖就可以了,跟安装到本地仓库的版本要一致.',0,2,1,0,0,'maven引入本地jar包','maven引入本地jar包',0,'2018-10-24 11:42:17','2018-10-24 20:38:17'),(39,'docker基础容器中安装java',1,'',NULL,1,'<ol>\n<li>下载对应系统的java版本到宿主机<br><a href=\"http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html\">http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html</a></li>\n<li>进入容器<br>docker exec -it &lt;容器名称或者ID&gt; bash</li>\n<li>将java压缩包从宿主机拷贝到容器指定目录<br>docker cp java路径 容器名称:容器中的路径</li>\n<li>解压<br>tar -zxvf  jdk-8u121-linux-x64.tar.gz</li>\n<li>创建java目录<br>mkdir /usr/lib/java</li>\n<li>将解压后的java剪切到该目录<br>cp 源文件路径  目标文件路径</li>\n<li>设置环境变量 vim ~/.bashrc<pre><code><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">export</span> JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/java/jdk1.8.0_121\n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">export</span> JRE_HOME=<span class=\"hljs-variable\">${JAVA_HOME}</span>/jre  \n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">export</span> CLASSPATH=.:<span class=\"hljs-variable\">${JAVA_HOME}</span>/lib:<span class=\"hljs-variable\">${JRE_HOME}</span>/lib  \n<span class=\"hljs-built_in\">export</span> PATH=<span class=\"hljs-variable\">${JAVA_HOME}</span>/bin:<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$PATH</span>\n</code></pre></li>\n<li>刷新环境变量<br>source ~/.bashrc</li>\n<li>验证<br>java -version</li>\n</ol>\n','1. 下载对应系统的java版本到宿主机\nhttp://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk8-downloads-2133151.html\n2. 进入容器\ndocker exec -it <容器名称或者ID> bash\n3. 将java压缩包从宿主机拷贝到容器指定目录\ndocker cp java路径 容器名称:容器中的路径\n4. 解压\ntar -zxvf  jdk-8u121-linux-x64.tar.gz\n5. 创建java目录\nmkdir /usr/lib/java\n6. 将解压后的java剪切到该目录\ncp 源文件路径  目标文件路径\n7. 设置环境变量 vim ~/.bashrc\n```\nexport JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/java/jdk1.8.0_121\nexport JRE_HOME=${JAVA_HOME}/jre  \nexport CLASSPATH=.:${JAVA_HOME}/lib:${JRE_HOME}/lib  \nexport PATH=${JAVA_HOME}/bin:$PATH \n```\n8. 刷新环境变量\nsource ~/.bashrc\n9. 验证\njava -version',0,6,1,0,1,'docker基础容器中安装java','docker基础容器中安装java',1,'2018-10-25 17:46:34','2018-10-25 17:46:34'),(40,'使用docker官方的mysql镜像',1,'',NULL,1,'<p><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/nzyalj/article/details/79177291\">https://blog.csdn.net/nzyalj/article/details/79177291</a></p>\n','https://blog.csdn.net/nzyalj/article/details/79177291',0,3,1,0,0,'使用docker官方的mysql镜像','使用docker官方的mysql镜像',0,'2018-10-25 17:49:38','2018-10-25 17:49:38');
